<item>
            <title>[HIVE-8830] hcatalog process don&apos;t exit because of non daemon thread</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-8830</link>
                <project id="12310843" key="HIVE">Hive</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;HiveClientCache has a cleanup thread which is not a daemon. It can cause hcat client process to hang even after the complete.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
